What this request does

- Executes the DeleteMysqlTitle mutation against {{HOST}} to remove a title record.

- Expects a valid title ID and returns the deleted title’s fields for verification.


Required variables

- {{HOST}}: GraphQL endpoint base URL (e.g., [https://your-backend/graphql](https://your-backend/graphql))

- {{titleId}}: The ID of the title to delete.


Authentication

- Inherit or apply the same auth as the collection/folder. If bearer/OAuth is required by your API, ensure the token is present (e.g., Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}). This request does not set auth locally.


GraphQL body (already configured)  
