deleteMysqlTitle(input: { id: "{{titleId}}" }) {  
titles {  
titleId  
titleType  
primaryTitle  
originalTitle  
isAdult  
startYear  
endYear  
runtimeMinutes  
}  
}  
}

Example responses

- Success (200):  
