- URL: {{HOST}}

- Protocol: GraphQL request body


Mutation

- updateMysqlTitle(input: { id, title { titleType, primaryTitle, originalTitle, isAdult, startYear, endYear, runtimeMinutes } })

- This request intentionally sets titleType to "tst" to trigger validation.


Variables

- This request does not use GraphQL variables; all fields are inlined in the mutation.

- Workspace variables referenced: {{HOST}}, {{access_token}}. Ensure your active environment defines these values.


